    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">風</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">かぜ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>ふき<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鳥</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">どり</span><span type="rp">）</span></span><lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">飛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">と</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>んでどこへゆく<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">海</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">うみ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>は<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">暴</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れているぞ。<lb />
<lb />
なんで<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鳴</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>く<lb />
かあかあ<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">山</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">やま</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>も<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">暴</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>れているぞ。<lb />
<lb />
あんなに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">高</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">たか</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>く<lb />
あんなに<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">低</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">ひく</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>く<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">後</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">あと</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>になり、<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">先</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">さき</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>になり。<lb />
<lb />
みんなから、きらわれて<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鳴</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>き<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">鳴</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">な</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>き<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">飛</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">と</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>んでゆく。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">黒</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">くろ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>い<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">衣</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">べべ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>を<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">着</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">き</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>かえて<lb />
こい。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">金</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">きん</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">帯</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おび</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>をしめて<lb />
こい。<lb />
<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">今度</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">こんど</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">世</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">よ</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>には<lb />
<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">王</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">おう</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>さまにしてやるぞ。<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
